name: Handicap-Accessible-One-Bedroom-Suite-One-Bedroom-Suite-Living-Room---View-from-Kitchenette
caption: One Bedroom Suite Living Room - View from Kitchenette
description: This living room includes a TV, dresser, sleeper sofa, arm chair, dining table with a chair, window, and coffee table,.
alt: On the left wall, a sleeper sofa sits opposite a suspended TV above a dresser. Between the two, a coffee table. On the back wall is a large window with a chair sitting in front of it. Opposite the window is a dining table with one chair seated at it.
